title: Local Hour: Hurricane Ian Relief
description:
We begin our Hurricane Ian Relief special in the place we all expected: The Executive Palace Hotel in Hialeah. Then, Mike Gesicki's role with the Dolphins, a potential Jae Crowder reunion in Miami, and Jeopardy! questions (and answers) about Mercury Morris. 
Go to worldofsuey.com/ian-relief to donate.
